name: Amber (Genshin Impact) LoRA
description:
!!! You need this extension in order to use this. Please follow the instructions on the github page to use.
https://github.com/kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks

This is a LoRA for Amber from Genshin Impact. The Flexible version is recommended.

More details:

https://huggingface.co/breakcore2/loras

Example images with prompts:

https://gist.github.com/breakcore2/0b2fcae494c5f38a22ef59486ec55682

When prompting for custom outfit:

amber \(genshin impact\), brown eyes, brown hair, long hair, red hair ribbon, (your outfit ideas here)

When prompting for her original outfit:

amber \(genshin impact\), brown eyes, brown hair, long hair, red hair ribbon, brown short shorts, leather gloves, pouch, thighhighs, white boots, medium breasts, cleavage cutout, shrug \(clothing\)

For her goggles:

goggles around neck, goggles on head
